Translated default messages and numeric formats validators for the jQuery validation plugin to pt-br
@version: v1.0.0
@author: Aldo Junior Carlos

#Usage:
Just include the plugin after jQuery validate plugin:
<head>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.1.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="../jquery.validate.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

    <script src="../jquery.validate.locate-pt-br.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body>
...
</body>
